    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/55b9c3f813beff5352088b3325e316c8.avif?t=1770827166\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br><br><br>Formula 2707 - All Stars Kombat 是一款战斗驾驶模拟器，其灵感来自 2000 年代的热门歌曲。它重现了经典的街机游戏动作，并提供没有速度限制的乐趣。<br><br><strong>旧式友谊</strong><br><br>Formula 2707 为那些错过与朋友在沙发上度过漫长夜晚的人提供了分屏多人游戏*模式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/92c5f7706bf3b774cb6b628ecef1ef8b.poster.avif?t=1770827166\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/92c5f7706bf3b774cb6b628ecef1ef8b.webm?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/92c5f7706bf3b774cb6b628ecef1ef8b.mp4?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>战斗模拟器</strong><br><br>Formula 2707 具有卡丁车游戏的所有特征，除了驾驶风格更偏向于模拟游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/0a522c7203d9723a337be77ce3e0f9ff.poster.avif?t=1770827166\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/0a522c7203d9723a337be77ce3e0f9ff.webm?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/0a522c7203d9723a337be77ce3e0f9ff.mp4?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>选择你的冠军</strong><br><br>在 Formula 2707 中，您可以解锁并与 12 位全明星冠军一起比赛。每种口味都有一个。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/c8eb8f93f13c30cbd3622673f9fca22e.poster.avif?t=1770827166\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/c8eb8f93f13c30cbd3622673f9fca22e.webm?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/c8eb8f93f13c30cbd3622673f9fca22e.mp4?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索银河系</strong><br><br>在 Formula 2707 中，您将通过探索游戏各个主角的不同星球，从深空到白雪皑皑的冰川，再到温暖的陆地海滩，面对最多样化的生物群落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/db95d4b956dd6460e3a9c96b96e84e5c.poster.avif?t=1770827166\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/db95d4b956dd6460e3a9c96b96e84e5c.webm?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/db95d4b956dd6460e3a9c96b96e84e5c.mp4?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏自定义</strong><br><br>Formula 2707 允许您根据自己的喜好自定义您的比赛，您可以更改：机器人数量、难度、圈数、比赛数量、PowerUps 或不。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/33e26e11d2b38908b83666ba70626c37.poster.avif?t=1770827166\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/33e26e11d2b38908b83666ba70626c37.webm?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253900/extras/33e26e11d2b38908b83666ba70626c37.mp4?t=1770827166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特点：</strong><br>[列表]<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>支持多种设备的可变图形质量<br></li><li>令人惊叹的老式分屏多人游戏，最多支持 4 名玩家*<br></li><li>12个可解锁角色<br></li><li>9 条可解锁曲目<br></li><li>9 辆可解锁的汽车<br></li><li>11 次通电<br></li><li>TimeMode：通过将您的名字添加到好友和全球排行榜来创造历史</li></ul><br>*至少需要一个控制器来玩分屏：每个玩家都需要自己的外围设备（操纵杆或控制器或键盘）",
